Dantaron.  The smooth cobblestones paving the wide, flat road make this the
premier route for transportation of goods out of the valley and north to the
Arien Road for connection to the cities of Earendam and Var Bandor.  The
road continues to the south, while uncultivated fields spread east and west
along the banks of the river.  
