#21411
The Dantaron Riverbank~
Directly to the north, the powerful Dantaron River flows eastwards in the
direction of Earendam and, ultimately, the Uthlin Ocean.  The clay of the
riverbank is slippery, but not too treacherous, and a few tenacious weeds
sprout from the earth, bedraggled and muddy.  Off to the west, the river is
spanned by a bridge, connecting the Arien and Lithling roads.  To the south,
the way into the Vale is veritably paved with lush fields of grass.  

